text: Trenton is the capital city of the U.S. state of New Jersey. It is the county seat of Mercer County. Trenton is in the middle part of New Jersey, along the Delaware River. == References == ==Other websites== Category:County seats in New Jersey Category:State capitals in the United States Category:1710s establishments in the Thirteen Colonies Category:18th-century establishments in New Jersey
title: Trenton, New Jersey
